.DT
query_person_payments
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
query_person_payments

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_person_payments -  This method makes a payment from one person to another.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
mixed query_person_payments(int value,
string place,
object payer,
object payee)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^value%^RESET%^ - the value to pay
%^BOLD%^place%^RESET%^ - the place to make the payment in
%^BOLD%^payer%^RESET%^ - the person the money is payed from
%^BOLD%^payee%^RESET%^ - the person the money is payed to
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
two element array, or 0 if it cannot be done

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/money_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method makes a payment from one person to another.
This method figures out what money should be given to the player
and what should be taken from the other to make a payment of the
correct value in the correct place.
.EP

